---
title: Cheesy Chicken Enchiladas Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: These cheesy chicken enchiladas come together in a snap, thanks to a few clever shortcuts. Making a filling with pre-cooked chicken keeps you away from the stove, and flavorful green salsa makes a perfect enchilada sauce. Thanks to the oven-ready tray that comes with your ingredients, even clean-up is a breeze—simply toss it when you're done!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6761a196bdfa7f79d1f16a22-540501eb.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6761a196bdfa7f79d1f16a22-en-US.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
author: Michelle Doll Olson
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cheesy-chicken-enchiladas-6761a196bdfa7f79d1f16a22
servings: 2
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 640 kcal
  fat: 33 g
